{"lemma":"عِراضِ","slug":"عِراضِ","root":"ع.ر.ض","root_slug":"ع-ر-ض","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ر-ض","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"عَرِيض","root":"عرض","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28702","n28703"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%90%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%B6%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"wide; broad"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"فَعِيل (faʕīl)-type stative-verb derived from the active participle from the verb عَرُضَ (ʕaruḍa, “to be or become wide”)."},"ipa":["/ʕa.riːdˤ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28702","headword_ar":"عُرَاضٌ","root":"ErD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EariyDN","text_ar":"عَرِيضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places:       -A2-  see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuroDN","text_ar":"عُرْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the latter half of the paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n28703","headword_ar":"عِرَاضٌ","root":"ErD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuroDN","text_ar":"عُرْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the first sentence, and again, in four places, in the latter half of the paragraph. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*a fiY EiraADi kalaAmihi","text_ar":"اَخَذَ فِى عِرَاضِ كَلَامِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He began to say the like of that which he"},{"kind":"text","text":"[another]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had said:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as in the O,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he matched him, and equalled him, by saying the like of what he had said."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaruwDN","text_ar":"عَرُوضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain brand;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K;) or, (K,) accord. to Yaakoob, (S, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a line upon the thigh of a camel, crosswise;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the neck, crosswise."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-Er-Rummánee, TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An iron with which the feet of a camel are marked in order that his foot-prints may be known."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.)"}],"source_refs":["K","S","O"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}